                private final ImageFromDockerfile apicurioDockerImage;



                private final ImageFromDockerfile apicurioContainerImage;






We should generally use "container image" instead of "Docker image" (here, and elsewhere). Docker is just one particular implementation used for creating OCI-compliant container images.

